<Link id="l00832" /><CodeLine lineNumber="832"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightKeywordFlow">for</span><span class="doxyHighlight"> (Index = 0; Index &lt; AddressZero.size() - 1; ++Index) &#123;</span></CodeLine>
